{
  "stem": "26142.15",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was-- you could see children, small children, with white flags, running alone, running out, outside trying to run out of the city.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It was a terrible, terrible sight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I remember this Pole-- Pole, he was saying-- he didn't know who we were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He-- he was talking to me in Polish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he was crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He says, this is already the 17 day that Warsaw is burning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] From there-- from there, we-- we worked around-- around the Vistula River in Modlin a month or-- or so.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It was supposed to be-- supposed to be put up-- put up a line of defense that the Germans and Hungarians would hold back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The Russians were pushing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "By-- by October, November, we were all the way down to the-- almost the city of Krakow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And-- what was that-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Over there, the-- the-- the Vistula River-- in Germany call it the Weichsel-- the Vistula River over there divides and there is a little island that is a few kilometers long.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And it-- it became that the Hungarians were supposed to hold this part of the Vistula River, because the Russians were on the other side.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the way the Russians were on that side of that side of the river, it was more like-- like they were on a-- on a hill.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And this side was in the valley.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we couldn't go there working, digging trenches on that island.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't go there during the day, because they could see us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would shoot across the-- across the-- the river.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we would work at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were stationed about five kilometers away from the river.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
